      • SitesRepository

        @Inject
public SitesRepository(CitiesRepository citiesRepository,
                                MapsRepository mapsRepository,
                                ToursRepository toursRepository)
        Constructs the basis of any DTORepository. Initializes the BeanRepository.bean's property and the BeanRepository.superBean with the passed dto as well as initializes BeanRepository.beansList. Constructor calls setupInitialBean(S) and startInternalInitialization().

      • requestSiteSaving

        public void requestSiteSaving()
        This method sends the server a request to create or update currently selected site. Created/Updated site gets a State.LOCKED state. i.e., it is not released to the public before before an employee with UserClassification of CONTENT_MANAGER and up approves the release of city this site's map belongs to.
